00:45:11,636 --> 00:45:14,480
<i>To everyone who made Hell on Wheels...</i>

543
00:45:14,505 --> 00:45:16,089
<i>And to everyone who loves it,</i>

544
00:45:16,114 --> 00:45:19,456
<i>AMC says thank you for a hell of a ride.</i>

